      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7611338143341447516, guid: 19237d723215ddf44bc643dd4ccb75b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: text.Array.size
      value: 7
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7611338143341447516, guid: 19237d723215ddf44bc643dd4ccb75b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'text.Array.data[0]'
      value: Aye, so you've met with the same fate.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7611338143341447516, guid: 19237d723215ddf44bc643dd4ccb75b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'text.Array.data[1]'
      value: Who are you?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7611338143341447516, guid: 19237d723215ddf44bc643dd4ccb75b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'text.Array.data[2]'
      value: 'Your predecessor. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7611338143341447516, guid: 19237d723215ddf44bc643dd4ccb75b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'text.Array.data[3]'
      value: 'No, they were lost in space. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7611338143341447516, guid: 19237d723215ddf44bc643dd4ccb75b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'text.Array.data[4]'
      value: Aye, some of us were, but I got crushed under that abomniable elevator,
        and now I'm here.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7611338143341447516, guid: 19237d723215ddf44bc643dd4ccb75b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'text.Array.data[5]'
      value: I'm going to try to find a way out.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7611338143341447516, guid: 19237d723215ddf44bc643dd4ccb75b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'text.Array.data[6]'
      value: HA HA HA! Good luck!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7611338143341447516, guid: 19237d723215ddf44bc643dd4ccb75b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: RightSpeaker.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7611338143341447516, guid: 19237d723215ddf44bc643dd4ccb75b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: textMetadata.Array.size
      value: 7
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7611338143341447516, guid: 19237d723215ddf44bc643dd4ccb75b6, type: 3}
